MS Dynamics Business Analyst Staines, Surrey £500 - £600 per day Myles Roberts Contract Posted 17 days ago Activate one-click apply. What is one-click apply? 2 x MS Dynamics CRM Functional Consultant/Busness Analyst required for an initial 6 month contract based in Staines.
The client is currently one of the largest users of Ms Dynamics CRM and are looking at rolling this our into all areas of their business. As a result they are looking to bring on 2 BAs /Functional Consultants to work in their project team.
You must be comfortable working with end users, gathering requirements, designing solutions and working with technical staff to deliver fit for purpose Dynamics CRM solutions.
You must have extensive experience with MS Dynamics CRM and ideally have worked with 365 (however earlier various will suffice).
If interested please apply with an updated CV as soon as possible. Due to the volume of applications, if you don't hear back withing 24 hours please consider your application unsuccessful on this occasion.
Any application /role related questions please get in touch via email.
Myles Roberts is acting as an Employment Business in relation to this vacancy.
